Planck Gravity · node GBR · GBR · At the smallest scale gravity comes back — and no one can write the theory. Where the very small is also massive (a black-hole core, the Big Bang), General Relativity and quantum mechanics must merge and the math gives infinities. The close bracket that won't close.

